      "content": "I'm so glad you're finally opening up about this. It's completely understandable that you're feeling overwhelmed and like you're just going through the motions to make others feel better. Your parents are coming from a place of love, but they don't realize that you're not just going through a phase, you're actually struggling with some deep-seated issues. Talking to someone is the first step towards healing, and I'm here to support you in finding the right resources and guidance. Have you considered reaching out to a therapist or counselor who specializes in mental health?",
